    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到《Salty Hounds》！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Salty Hounds》</strong>是一款开放世界约会模拟游戏，你将在这里创造自己的爱情故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>(*直播指南详见文末)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/1aa3e281190a3e40d80764762575993f.poster.avif?t=1749387172\" width=800 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/1aa3e281190a3e40d80764762575993f.webm?t=1749387172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/1aa3e281190a3e40d80764762575993f.mp4?t=1749387172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/f6a8692e42cf1281c7ec8debf54ff896.poster.avif?t=1749387172\" width=800 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/f6a8692e42cf1281c7ec8debf54ff896.webm?t=1749387172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/f6a8692e42cf1281c7ec8debf54ff896.mp4?t=1749387172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/b88f49997c711cb6df90bbfb913fe6fa.avif?t=1749387172\" width=620 height=348 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >恋爱对象</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个恋爱对象都有自己的日常日程、喜好和等待被揭开的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/3fcc49cc5b8f567b5ea48508e0a2cf83.avif?t=1749387172\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras_big/3fcc49cc5b8f567b5ea48508e0a2cf83.avif?t=1749387172 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/ee5810a6498c58d42568f9dc2d3daa47.avif?t=1749387172\" width=620 height=348 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在父亲遭遇事故后，你接管了一家小型保镖机构 Salty Hounds。通过日常互动、特别活动和浪漫约会，遇见你的心仪对象并赢得他们的芳心。在充满活力的开放世界城市中享受浪漫生活，该城市拥有完整的昼夜循环系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/94b98e0029b6baa3b9457798588fe675.poster.avif?t=1749387172\" width=600 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/94b98e0029b6baa3b9457798588fe675.webm?t=1749387172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/94b98e0029b6baa3b9457798588fe675.mp4?t=1749387172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到心仪对象，与他们交谈，了解他们并随着时间的推移建立关系。你们成为朋友并赢得他们的信任之后，你可以解锁新的事件和浪漫对话。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/b108e863b2312410504c7ff482d89220.avif?t=1749387172\" width=620 height=348 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 沉浸式的开放世界和高质量像素艺术中流畅的动画角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 许多精美的手绘插图和角色插画</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 由韩国知名声优录制的大量语音内容（后续还将添加更多）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 随着好感度和其他属性的变化，NPC 会出现动态对话</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 享受城市各处的随机偶遇和提升技能的活动</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/68389d0cf540279dcdb04950fa09160e.poster.avif?t=1749387172\" width=620 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/68389d0cf540279dcdb04950fa09160e.webm?t=1749387172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/68389d0cf540279dcdb04950fa09160e.mp4?t=1749387172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>与五位独具魅力的角色谈一场恋爱！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >♥ 诺如，首席保镖</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/b42fbc53346e673dd1fa689e2f6be92d.avif?t=1749387172\" width=614 height=114 /></span><i>“我不记得我们之前有这么亲密无间。”</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位冷漠到几乎反社会的独行侠，但却拥有优秀的实战经验的保镖。尽管他是你儿时的朋友，但他现在似乎不太习惯有你在身边。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>♥ 世赫，竞争对手公司老板</strong> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/e25127f69f5946f564418a8bc805a52b.avif?t=1749387172\" width=614 height=114 /></span><i>“这真的是你应该问‘对手’的问题吗？”</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >竞争对手公司“海亮安保”的年轻有为的CEO。既温柔又冷酷无情，是一位不可小觑的对手。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>♥ 泰旻，开朗的保镖</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/7581e45c9cdf49295c11b20b29d58c27.avif?t=1749387172\" width=614 height=114 /></span><i>“什么？三倍加班费？我马上就到！”</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位诙谐风趣、充满个人魅力的保镖，拥有温柔却强大的领导能力。虽然你已经习惯了他的自由奔放的性格，但还是希望他至少在工作时系上领带。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>♥ 有真，犯罪调查员 </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/17736eccaf14991fdba3becc87532bbe.avif?t=1749387172\" width=614 height=114 /></span><i>“现在你有权保持沉默。”</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位能力出色的犯罪调查员，立志创造一个没有不公正的世界。他曾是你的私人家教，但那已经是很久以前的事了。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>♥ 俊昊，天真的保镖</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876460/extras/cc1b15278784ae4d4c8f546a295a317a.avif?t=1749387172\" width=614 height=114 /></span><i>“你不会从我的工资里扣热水费？真的吗？”</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位天真浪漫，但被骗到一家黑心安保公司工作的保镖，每天都在被各种敲诈勒索。或许你应该帮帮他？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>直播指南:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为防止剧情剧透，请各位主播将各角色的直播内容限制在好感度等级1～2级以内！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请在直播标题中加入“抢先体验 / Early Access&quot; 字样，并附上我们的Steam商店页面链接。 </p></li></ul>",
